{"tid":1979291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【眼科醫生 · 有眼無珠】林順潮撐世衞盡責 吹噓武漢為世界犧牲","createTime":"2020-04-19T10:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T10:25:16.000Z","uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e10896a2ce763b3b3b6a12e5a907f94e4ee1d7ca","tid":1979291,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:21:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眼科醫生 &middot; 有眼無珠】<br />\n撐世衞盡責 吹噓武漢為世界犧牲</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n節錄自2020年4月19日香港蘋果日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1WXjV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1WXjV7.jpg&h=be89c5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">▲眼科醫生兼港區全國人大代表林順潮</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼科醫生兼港區全國人大代表林順潮指，自己於2003年沙士期間在威爾斯親王醫院工作，認為世衞今次抗疫期間已做了大量工作，反應合適及負責任，指坊間很多批評都只是「事後孔明」，因病毒充滿不確定性，又讚賞武漢當時及時封城，「好大犧牲經濟各方面，為世界換嚟2個月嘅準備。」他又指中國於1月12日在網上公佈病毒基因圖譜，令現時美國研發疫苗速度加快，惟相信病毒基因會出現變異，疫苗或會有抗藥性，市民要有心理準備將會是一場持久戰。"},{"pid":"8971ea1872011c6afce7e013486ba0cbbd0de432","tid":1979291,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"李文亮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea7d58940c18e8e99bb8d1582aed5f22551378b","tid":1979291,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"人一藍"},{"pid":"cfea9265688a7027ffd887901d21c3d63aba1ebc","tid":1979291,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bea7d58940c18e8e99bb8d1582aed5f22551378b","tid":1979291,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"人一藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:25:16.000Z","msg":"無腦兼有眼無珠冚家剷醫棍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}